%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/Kh%C3%A1nh-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%E1%BA%ADn-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-lWJ1ARdnRJ4Xu-BCrgdYZQ">Khánh Nguyễn Vận Đồng sinh nhật kỳ 1 - 慶阮運同生日其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%E1%BA%ADm-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%ADch/poem-aABgyHVenOrJ4rb5ssziXA">Nguyễn Thiên Tích - 阮天錫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%E1%BA%ADm-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-0WkoGT1eLc4Wm2cpSboCUw">Hà Nhậm Đại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/Ti%C3%AAn-Du-s%C6%A1n-V%E1%BA%A1n-Ph%C3%BAc-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-BSGDQTSKqkUEyVRycJ0VfQ">Tiên Du sơn Vạn Phúc tự - 仙遊山萬福寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/author-jcnyctA2yI9a8upP-Bt9aw">Nguyễn Sưởng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
